Installing hpcviewer
====================

* Uncompress the tar file 
	tar xzf hpcviewer-......tgz.
* Run install script:
	install [hpctoolkit_installation_directory]

This will install the hpcviewer executable and its components in 
[hpctoolkit_installation_directory]

* To run the viewer, type:

	[hpctoolkit_installation_directory]/bin/hpcviewer


Notes
====================

* By default, the configuration files are located in 
  $USER/.hpctoolkit/hpcviewer/<platform>/
* To reset the configuration, you need to remove this directory.

